-- Kuwait's Boubyan Bank Reports $4.9 Million Second-Quarter Net After Loss
-- Fiona MacDonald
-- 2010-07-27T05:36:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/kuwait-s-boubyan-bank-reports-4-9-million-second-quarter-net-after-loss.html

          
          
             Boubyan Bank KSC, an Islamic lender
in Kuwait, reported a second-quarter profit of 1.4 million 
dinars after a loss in the same period last year, according to 
a statement on the Kuwait Stock Exchange Web site today.  
